    <h1 class="fw-bold">Getting Started</h1>
    <p>Finding a problem to solve can sometimes be a difficult starting point. You can choose to design a solution for one of the 
        problems listed below or do some research to identify a different problem. Conduct research to explore existing solutions 
        to the problem and to determine what challenges are still faced. You may want to create something new or improve on an 
        existing solution; that's what innovation is all about.</p>
    
